<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='390000' id='t-390000'>but ultimately, six hours a day, five days a week</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='393000' id='t-393000'>they're spending in a classroom,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='395000' id='t-395000'>and most of those classrooms</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='397000' id='t-397000'>are not places where men exist.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='399000' id='t-399000'>And so they say, I guess this really isn't a place for boys.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='402000' id='t-402000'>This is a place for girls.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='404000' id='t-404000'>And I'm not very good at this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='406000' id='t-406000'>so I guess I'd better</span>
