<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>Men don't belong here, that's pretty obvious.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='415000' id='t-415000'>So that may be a very direct way</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='417000' id='t-417000'>that we see it happen.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419000' id='t-419000'>But less directly,</span>
