</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480000' id='t-480000'>The reason that this is a problem</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='483000' id='t-483000'>is because the message that boys are getting</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486000' id='t-486000'>is &quot;you need to do</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488000' id='t-488000'>what the teacher asks you to do all the time.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491000' id='t-491000'>The teacher's salary depends</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494000' id='t-494000'>on &quot;No Child Left Behind&quot; and &quot;Race to the Top&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='496000' id='t-496000'>and accountability and testing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='498000' id='t-498000'>and all of this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500000' id='t-500000'>So she has to figure out a way</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='502000' id='t-502000'>to get all these boys through this curriculum --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='505000' id='t-505000'>and girls.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='507000' id='t-507000'>This compressed curriculum is bad</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509000' id='t-509000'>for all active kids.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='512000' id='t-512000'>And what happens is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='514000' id='t-514000'>she says, &quot;Please, sit down,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517000' id='t-517000'>be quiet, do what you're told, follow the rules,</span>
