<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='522000' id='t-522000'>be a girl.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='524000' id='t-524000'>That's what she tells them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526000' id='t-526000'>Indirectly, that's what she tells them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529000' id='t-529000'>And so this is a very serious problem. Where is it coming from?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531000' id='t-531000'>It's coming from us.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533000' id='t-533000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='536000' id='t-536000'>We want our babies to read when they are six months old.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='539000' id='t-539000'>Have you seen the ads?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='541000' id='t-541000'>We want to live in Lake Wobegon</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543000' id='t-543000'>where every child is above average,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='546000' id='t-546000'>but what this does to our children is really not healthy.</span>
