<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='596000' id='t-596000'>Do they make sense?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='598000' id='t-598000'>We need to think about</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='600000' id='t-600000'>how to uncompress this curriculum if we can,</span>
