<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='605000' id='t-605000'>that is comfortable for them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='607000' id='t-607000'>All of those conversations need to be happening.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='609000' id='t-609000'>There are some great examples out there</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='611000' id='t-611000'>of schools --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='613000' id='t-613000'>the New York Times just talked about a school recently.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='615000' id='t-615000'>A game designer from the New School</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='618000' id='t-618000'>put together a wonderful video gaming school.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='621000' id='t-621000'>But it only treats a few kids,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='624000' id='t-624000'>and so this isn't very scalable.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='626000' id='t-626000'>We have to change the culture and the feelings</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='628000' id='t-628000'>that politicians and school board members and parents have</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631000' id='t-631000'>about the way we accept and what we accept</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633000' id='t-633000'>in our schools today.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='636000' id='t-636000'>We need to find more money for game design.</span>
