<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='671000' id='t-671000'>or whatever it is that they get.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='673000' id='t-673000'>And they're always talking about this stuff.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='675000' id='t-675000'>And they say these things as if it's okay.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='677000' id='t-677000'>But if it were your culture,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='679000' id='t-679000'>think of how that might feel.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='681000' id='t-681000'>It's very uncomfortable to be on the receiving end</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='683000' id='t-683000'>of that kind of language.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='685000' id='t-685000'>They're nervous about anything</span>
